&lt;h1 id="git"&gt;git&lt;a href="#git" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="Link to this section"&gt;&lt;svg class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"&gt;&lt;g fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"&gt;&lt;path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/&gt;&lt;path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;h1 id="introduction-to-git---brief-history-reasons-for-use-and-what-is-version-control"&gt;Introduction to Git - Brief History, Reasons for Use, and What is Version Control?&lt;a href="#introduction-to-git---brief-history-reasons-for-use-and-what-is-version-control" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="Link to this section"&gt;&lt;svg class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"&gt;&lt;g fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"&gt;&lt;path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/&gt;&lt;path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;History: Released under the GPL license in 2005, created by Linus Torvalds.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reason for use: When collaborating as a team, using git commands enables real-time updates without the hassle of the traditional method of uploading to the cloud and then downloading again.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Version control: Software that helps track code changes over a period of time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1 id="explanation-of-version-control-logic"&gt;Explanation of Version Control Logic&lt;a href="#explanation-of-version-control-logic" class="heading-anchor" aria-label="Link to this section"&gt;&lt;svg class="h-4 w-4" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"&gt;&lt;g fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"&gt;&lt;path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/&gt;&lt;path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;
